Travels New Zealand 2009 Cutelings

Cutelings

On the trip to New Zealand we encountered many critters. The native critters (i.e. birds) were interesting but we spent the most time playing with ducklings and a kitten.

  • A cheeky alpine parrot or Kea
  • Little birdy watching us swim at Lake Ianthe
  • A puffy bird hiding from the rain
